title: Super Bowl LV Preview and Stafford-Goff Fallout
description:
Cole and Ryan are joined by The Ringer's Kaelen Jones to preview Super Bowl LV (00:31) and discuss how to stop the potent offenses of the Chiefs and Bucs. Later, the guys discuss the fallout of the Stafford-Goff trade (35:06) and how it could affect Deshaun Watson's future (42:12).
Hosts: Cole Wright and Ryan Shazier
Guest: Kaelen Jones
